data.description: Remarkable immaculate 4 bdr/3bath energy smart home in The Shadows at Manchac. The RAPHAEL III model offers an open floorplan with a formal dining area great for hosting elegant gatherings. As you step inside, you are greeted by a spacious and inviting interior. Special features include a living room with custom blinds , wood floors, gas fireplace, and a wall of windows that allows natural lighting to stream in. Large kitchen with 3cm granite on island and counter tops, stainless appliances, and undermount sink. Kitchen also has upgraded lighting featuring under cabinet lighting and a modern state of the art light fixture in breakfast area. Granite counters in baths and 16 inch tile flooring in all wet areas. Custom tile shower with glass door in primary bath. Energy efficient features include a tankless hot water heater, radiant barrier decking in attic, and low E-3 double insulated windows. Covered patio in rear for relaxing evenings. Plenty of parking with double car garage and driveway. Great schools featuring Oakgrove Primary . Floodzone X . Seller is very motivated and open to providing a Seller Credit to buy down interest rate. Come see this beauty today and check out virtual tour at https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=4KL8f342LfS
